OL,3,CMan guilty of killing wife in retrial
OL,4,Cas child reveals murder plot 8 years on
OL,6,FA man who walked free for the murder
OL,7,Fof his wife eight years ago, has now
OL,8,Fbeen found guilty after his child
OL,9,Frevealed he had plotted the attack.
OL,11,FRobert Rhodes, 52, was convicted of
OL,12,Fthe murder of his estranged wife, Dawn
OL,13,FRhodes, on Friday after the jury
OL,14,Freturned a unanimous verdict,
OL,15,Ffollowing an eight-week re-trial at
OL,16,Fthe Inner Crown Court in London.
