OL,3,CMan guilty of killing wife in retrial
OL,4,Cas child reveals murder plot 8 years on
OL,6,FHe was previously found not guilty
OL,7,Fafter a trial at the Old Bailey in
OL,8,F2017, where he convinced jurors that
OL,9,Fhe had acted in self-defence during an
OL,10,Fargument.
OL,12,FThe guilty verdict comes after the
OL,13,Fcouple's child, who cannot be named
OL,14,Ffor legal reasons, came forward with
OL,15,Fnew evidence that Rhodes had killed
OL,16,Fhis wife and that they were involved
OL,17,Fin the murder.
OL,19,FThey were a key witness during the
OL,20,Ftrial when Rhodes was acquitted.
