OL,3,CMan guilty of killing wife in retrial
OL,4,Cas child reveals murder plot 8 years on
OL,6,FIn November 2021 , the child told
OL,7,Ftheir therapist that their father had
OL,8,Fplanned to kill Dawn and had
OL,9,Fmanipulated them into being involved
OL,10,Fin it.
OL,12,FAccording to the child, Rhodes
OL,13,Fdescribed it as "our plan" and then
OL,14,Fmade them lie about how their mother
OL,15,Fhad died.
OL,17,FFollowing an application to the Court
OL,18,Fof Appeal in November 2024, the
OL,19,Facquittal was quashed, and permission
OL,20,Fwas granted for a retrial for the
OL,21,Foffence of murder.
