OL,6,FAlongside perjury and perverting the
OL,7,Fcourse of justice, Rhodes was also
OL,8,Ffound guilty of child cruelty by
OL,9,Finflicting a wound to a child under 10
OL,10,Fin an attempt to cover up this crime.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, the court heard how,
OL,13,Fbefore Dawn's death, the marriage
OL,14,Fbetween her and Rhodes had been
OL,15,Fdifficult and that he had filed for
OL,16,Fdivorce.
