OL,6,FAt 7.34 pm on June 2, 2016 the child
OL,7,Fmade a 999 call to the police, during
OL,8,Fwhich Rhodes said his wife attacked
OL,9,Fhim and their child with a knife at
OL,10,Ftheir home in Surrey, and that he
OL,11,Facted in self-defence.
OL,13,FPolice found Dawn lying on the kitchen
OL,14,Ffloor. Her throat had been cut to the
OL,15,Fextent that it had severed all the
OL,16,Fstructures in her neck.
OL,18,FRhodes claims Dawn attacked him in a
OL,19,Fpolice interview in 2016
