OL,4,Cas child reveals murder plot 8 years on
OL,6,FRhodes told police that Dawn had hit
OL,7,Fhim twice on the back of the head. The
OL,8,Fchild showed officers a deep
OL,9,Flaceration to their arm, which they
OL,10,Fsaid had been done by their mother.
OL,12,FRhodes was arrested for murder that
OL,13,Fevening.
OL,15,FDuring his police interview, he said
OL,16,Fthat he and Dawn had been arguing in
OL,17,Fthe kitchen when she picked up a knife
OL,18,Fand swung it towards the child, at
OL,19,Fwhich point he told the child to go
OL,20,Fupstairs.
