OL,6,FHe said he took the knife from Dawn
OL,7,Fand that she came at him in a fury,
OL,8,Fand he swung at her with the knife,
OL,9,Fmaking contact with her neck, before
OL,10,Fhe ran upstairs and called the police.
OL,12,FWhen the child was interviewed, they
OL,13,Fgave an account consistent with the
OL,14,Fone Rhodes had given as to how the
OL,15,Finjuries they had suffered had been
OL,16,Finflicted.
OL,18,FRhode being interviewed by police in
OL,19,F2024 after the new evidence came to
