OL,4,Cas child reveals murder plot 8 years on
OL,6,FFollowing a lengthy investigation,
OL,7,FRhodes was charged with murder and
OL,8,Fstood trial in May 2017. A few days
OL,9,Flater, the jury reached a majority
OL,10,Fverdict, finding Rhodes not guilty of
OL,11,Fmurder.
OL,13,FAfter coming forward in November 2021,
OL,14,Fthe child was interviewed and
OL,15,Fdescribed how their father had caused
OL,16,Fthe relationship with their mother to
OL,17,Fdeteriorate.
