OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,7,FChief Inspector Kimball Edey, from the
OL,8,FSurrey and Sussex Police Major Crime
OL,9,FTeam, said: "During the first trial,
OL,10,FDawn was portrayed as the villain, but
OL,11,Fhad actually been a victim of domestic
OL,12,Fabuse and coercive control at the
OL,13,Fhands of her husband for years.
