OL,3,CMan guilty of killing wife in retrial
OL,4,Cas child reveals murder plot 8 years on
OL,6,F"The fact that Rhodes not only
OL,7,Fmurdered his wife in cold blood but
OL,8,Fthen manipulated and groomed his own
OL,9,Fchild to play a part in his evil
OL,10,Fscheme and cover up what he had done
OL,11,Fis simply despicable - not only did he
OL,12,Ftake a life; he irreparably damaged
OL,13,Fanother, as well as the lives of
OL,14,Feveryone else who loved Dawn.
OL,16,F"The fact that the child came forward
OL,17,Fnine years after their mother's death
OL,18,Fto tell the truth about what happened
OL,19,Fis remarkable and shows enormous
OL,20,Fbravery.
