OL,3,CMan guilty of killing wife in retrial
OL,4,Cas child reveals murder plot 8 years on
OL,6,F"While it should be acknowledged that
OL,7,Fthe child was under the age of
OL,8,Fcriminal responsibility at the time of
OL,9,FDawn's death and that they were not
OL,10,Fresponsible for the acts that Rhodes
OL,11,Fmanipulated them into doing, the
OL,12,Frealisation that they were complicit
OL,13,Fin Dawn's death and coming forward to
OL,14,Fset the record straight nine years
OL,15,Flater, is nothing short of
OL,16,Fextraordinary."
OL,18,FRobert Rhodes will be sentenced at
OL,19,FInner London Crown Court on January
OL,20,F16, 2026.
