OL,6,FDawn's families issued statements
OL,7,Ffollowing the verdict.
OL,9,FHer mother, Liz Spencer, and sister,
OL,10,FKirsty said: "In murdering Dawn, he
OL,11,Ftook away a kind-hearted person whose
OL,12,Flife and generosity of spirit was
OL,13,Fnever-ending. Despite the fact that
OL,14,Fhis lies and deception were for so
OL,15,Flong believed by so many we knew the
OL,16,Ftruth in our hearts and souls.
