OL,6,FDawn's brother Darren said: "There are
OL,7,Fno words we can use to make sense of
OL,8,Fthis horrific situation. We struggle
OL,9,Fto comprehend the mindset of an
OL,10,Findividual so twisted as to even
OL,11,Fcontemplate this as a solution to his
OL,12,Fown unhappiness, implicating a child
OL,13,Funder 10 in the process. The lack of
OL,14,Fforesight and disregard not only for
OL,15,Fhis own family but also for the wider,
OL,16,Fextended family is beyond belief."
